                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10107" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2544</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">264 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">筑基信息化转型：群峰机械数据中台赋能之旅</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Transformation of Information Technology: Qunfeng Machinery&#39;s Data Centre Empowerment Journey</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">林春培，王惠玲，李雅雯，程晔，林倩雯，汤睿，张建海，许先杰，林恒阳</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华侨大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福建群峰机械有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">信息管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械制造业；信息化转型；数据中台；信息孤岛</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Mechanical Manufacturing, Informational transformation, Data Centre, Information Silos</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在工业物联网与数字孪生技术深度渗透的背景下，如何突破信息孤岛、系统割裂与组织壁垒，构建全链路贯通的智能生产体系，已成为传统机械制造企业信息化转型的核心挑战。作为离散型装备制造领域的龙头企业，群峰机械积极响应国家“十四五”智能智能制造规划的政策导向，历经二十余年的探索，成功走出了一条以数据中台为驱动、以“战略锚定—系统重构—生态跃迁”为路径的信息化转型之路。本案例系统呈现了这一转型路径：首先，群峰精准锚定了全球市场拓展与供应链优化的核心战略目标；随即重构业务协同平台及车间物联网，达成设备全面互联；最终依托强大的数据中台，打通了从设计到生产的全流程数据通道，成功实现生态跃迁。此外，本案例以群峰机械的转型实践为蓝本，总结其从传统制造迈向信息化升级的经验教训，旨在培养学生理论应用、信息处理和创新解决问题的能力，并为同类型企业在信息化转型和数据中台建设方面提供参考与借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the context of the deep penetration of industrial Internet of Things and digital twin technologies, breaking through information silos, system fragmentation, and organizational barriers to build an intelligent production system that spans the entire value chain has become the core challenge for traditional mechanical manufacturing enterprises in their digital transformation. As a leading enterprise in the discrete equipment manufacturing sector, Qunfeng Machinery has actively responded to the policy direction of the national “14th Five-Year Plan” for intelligent manufacturing. As a leading enterprise in the discrete equipment manufacturing sector, Qunfeng Machinery has actively responded to the policy direction of the national “14th Five-Year Plan” for intelligent manufacturing.After over two decades of exploration, we have successfully charted a path of digital transformation driven by a data middleware platform,following a strategic framework of “strategic alignment—system restructuring—ecological transformation.”This case study systematically illustrates this transformation path: first, Qunfeng precisely anchored its core strategic objectives of global market expansion and supply chain optimization; then, it restructured its business collaboration platform and workshop IoT to achieve full connectivity of equipment; finally, leveraging a powerful data middleware platform, it established a seamless data channel across the entire process from design to production, successfully achieving an ecological leap.Furthermore, this case study draws on Qunfeng Machinery&#39;s transformation practices to summarize lessons learned in transitioning from traditional manufacturing to information technology upgrades. It aims to cultivate students&#39; abilities in theoretical application, information processing, and innovative problem-solving, while providing reference and insights for similar enterprises in their information technology transformation and data middleware platform construction efforts.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《信息化创新与转型》、《管理信息系统》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数据中台理论；数据治理理论。</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-11</td>
                            </tr>
